high_descs: Walk across the room to the kitchen sinks and turn right to face it.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle that is on the counter in front of the sinks.
Turn around and walk across the room to the end of the white table and turn left to face it.
Slice up the potato that is to the right of the coffee machine.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the sinks.
Place the large metal knife on the counter in front of the leftmost sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to the white table and then turn left to face it.
Pick up the end slice of the potato.
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sinks.
Put the potato slice in the left sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and pick the potato slice back up.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and take a step forward, turn right again to face the kitchen counter.
Place the clean potato slice on the counter in front of the leftmost sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, then right, go forward as far as sink, turn right to face sink.
Pick up yellow-handled knife from front of the left hand sink.
Turn right, turn right, cross room to white table, turn left to face it.
Slice the potato on the table.
Turn left, turn left, turn right, walk to the sink.
Place knife down in front of the left hand sink.
Turn right, turn right, cross room to white table, turn left to face it.
Pick up the closest slice of potato from the table.
Turn left, cross room to the sink.
Put potato in sink, fill sink with water, empty sink, take potato from sink.
Turn around clockwise to face the sink.
Place potato in front of the left hand sink behind the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a washed potato slice in front of the left hand sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the right side of the table.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to the right side of the table.
Slice the potato on the table.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right, move to the right side of the table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the potato slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of potato on the counter.

high_descs: walk to the sink at the end of the room on the right
grab the knife off of the kitchen counter ledge in front of the sink
turn around and walk over to the small white table at the end of the room, then turn left to face it
slice up the potato on the right side of the coffee maker
turn left and walk to the kitchen sink at the end of the room
place the knife down on the kitchen counter ledge in front of the sink
turn around and walk back over to the table at the end of the room
grab a potato slice off of the table there
turn left and walk to the sink ahead
place the potato slice in the sink and clean it off, then pick it up again
back up from the sink and face it again
place the potato slice on the kitchen counter in front of the sink near the knife
anns.task_desc: place a clean potato slice on the kitchen sink ledge

high_descs: Go forward and face the sink on your right.
Take the knife by the sink in front of you.
Turn around, then left to face the table on your left.
Slice the potato on the table in front of you.
Turn left and head towards the sink in front of you.
Place the knife by the sink in front of you.
Turn around, then left to face the table on your left.
Take a potato slice from the table in front of you
Turn left and head towards the sink in front of you.
Wash the potato in the sink and take it out.
Turn around in a circle and face the sink.
Put the potato slice by the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Clean a potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room and turn to the right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn around, walk across the room, turn left to face the table.
Cut the potato on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the sink.
Place the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn around, walk across the room, turn left to face the table.
Pick up a potato slice from on the table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the sink.
Clean the potato in the sink and then pick it up.
Step back and face the edge of the sink.
Put the potato slice on the edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Clean a potato slice as well as put it on the edge of the sink.
